### GET all tasks by account id
GET {{path}}?accountId={{accountId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET by id
GET {{path}}/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### POST create new task
POST {{path}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

