### PUT update task
PUT {{path}}/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "taskId": "{{taskId}}",
  "accountId":  "{{accountId}}",
  "title": "Test UPDATED",
  "body": "Test UPDATED",
  "completed": true
}

### DELETE by id
